Title: Part 10: Gondor
Text:
The Black Gate will be too well guarded...
But maybe Gollum knows another way!

Apparently I have to cross the middle of the war zone in Gondor!...
I also met the young captain Faramir.
I hope he comes to his senses and lets me go.
CompleteText:
Faramir took me to Osgliath.
The once beautiful city of Gondor which now resembles a war ruin...

It's far too dangerous to be here, I must convince Faramir to let me go.
